    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>If you or a loved one have been impacted by</strong><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324450/extras/10610ac2dec8086d063030b9d05a1b36.avif?t=1730830059\" width=150 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>then you may be entitled to play this game.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Overview-</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bullet Syndrome takes place in 4 Large infested worlds filled with differing enemies. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upon defeating Minibosses located in these maps and surviving 15 enemy waves, you may challenge the big boss.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hunt regular enemies for cash-</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324450/extras/ae3ae5df96f2ce73a52db391f05655ce.poster.avif?t=1730830059\" width=200 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324450/extras/ae3ae5df96f2ce73a52db391f05655ce.webm?t=1730830059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324450/extras/97cc3c12818cc542a9fac1a2c5a5ae40.apng?t=1730830059\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324450/extras/97cc3c12818cc542a9fac1a2c5a5ae40.poster.avif?t=1730830059\" class=\"bb_img\" width=100 height=100 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enemies will drop money depending on their hp. the more damage you can deal, the more money can be obtained.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Use cash to purchase tickets-</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324450/extras/7265c7e138f5e544a2df9b4295fccb9f.poster.avif?t=1730830059\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324450/extras/7265c7e138f5e544a2df9b4295fccb9f.webm?t=1730830059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tickets may summon a strong enemy that will drop base weapons, different maps will have different base weapons you can attain from them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Alchemy-</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The alchemist will help you turn base materials into higher weapons :</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324450/extras/4b9549c839d2a61a298ab5e2b775903c.apng?t=1730830059\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324450/extras/4b9549c839d2a61a298ab5e2b775903c.poster.avif?t=1730830059\" class=\"bb_img\" width=239 height=209 /></picture></span>                             <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324450/extras/cbbcac717762e476308a48dcf506d6f4.poster.avif?t=1730830059\" width=100 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324450/extras/cbbcac717762e476308a48dcf506d6f4.webm?t=1730830059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And further past that :</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324450/extras/f578cf1e325d9f1c17feab6a5078d299.apng?t=1730830059\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324450/extras/f578cf1e325d9f1c17feab6a5078d299.poster.avif?t=1730830059\" class=\"bb_img\" width=294 height=252 /></picture></span>                 <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324450/extras/cb5672526784a905ece962ab4e5cbd13.apng?t=1730830059\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324450/extras/cb5672526784a905ece962ab4e5cbd13.poster.avif?t=1730830059\" class=\"bb_img\" width=100 height=100 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >In the end-</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cull the weakest, battle the strongest, then you may challenge me.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324450/extras/f4b1cce881b460ef3bccb4757568d68a.webp?t=1730830059\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324450/extras/f4b1cce881b460ef3bccb4757568d68a.poster.avif?t=1730830059\" class=\"bb_img\" width=500 height=500 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
